      "content": "hey, quick question... im on sertraline for my depression but finals week is coming up and i'm feeling super low and unmotivated. i was thinking about adding some st johns wort to my routine to help with my mood. is it okay to take them both together? i dont want to mess anything up but i really need a boost",
