      "content": "wait, \"serotonin overload\" sounds kind of scary lol. like, is it actually dangerous? i was just thinking since st johns wort is just a plant and it's natural it would be a safe way to supplement what the sertraline is already doing. i've heard it works really well for people. is it really that big of an issue or just a precaution?",
